    "Title": "Eliminate Sentries",
    "Description": "It appears the UEE are stepping up their efforts to stop our movement. One of our pilots discovered a few orbital sentries and ships at ~mission(location|address). We believe they\u2019re part of a UEE espionage campaign targeting XenoThreat and it's vital that it be stopped before they gather anything that could harm our ongoing efforts.\n\nWe\u2019re looking for a skilled merc willing to eliminate this threat and stop this invasion of privacy before it spreads even further. Who knows how much bigger this operation will get if it\u2019s not taken off-line immediately? Payment will make it worth your while and be sent promptly once everything is blown to bits. \n\nSee it done, and help be a part of the right side of history.\n\nComm. Spec. Engler",
